form.name.value;\n  if (!email || !password || !postcode || !name){\n    showAlert(\"All fields required\");\n    ev.preventDefault();\n    return false;\n  }\n  else if (!validateEmail(email)){\n 3){\n    return false;\n  }\n  else if (!re.exec(email)){\n    return false;\n  }\n  return true;\n}\nfunction validateName(name){\n  // Name must have at least one space with non-whitespace
